query:
SELECT
                        system_id,
                        manufacturing,
                        reaction
                    FROM industry_index
                    WHERE timestamp = (
                        SELECT timestamp
                        FROM industry_index
                        WHERE system_id = ANY($1)
                        GROUP BY system_id, timestamp
                        ORDER BY timestamp DESC
                        LIMIT 1
                    )
                    AND system_id = ANY($1)
